screen_desc: The screenshot shows a mobile app interface for searching an address. At the top, there is a search bar with a magnifying glass icon and the placeholder text "Search for an address." Below the search bar, there is a section titled "Nearby addresses" with an option to "Use current location" and a prompt to "Enable Location Services." The status bar at the top of the screen shows the time as 11:24 AM, along with various icons indicating notifications, network status, and battery level.
